      takeaway: "The spiral is loss, then bigger bet, then bigger loss, and it ends more accounts than bad picks ever have. Write your circuit breakers while you are calm, because the tilted version of you will not. Two losses in a day means you are done for the day, with no exceptions, and especially not on the days you most want one.",
